    "subTabDescription": "<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p><strong>Ski Equipment</strong></p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"566\" style=\"height: 244px; width: 567px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<th style=\"height: 21px; width: 211px;\">6 days</th>\n<th style=\"height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Category</th>\n<th style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">\n<p>Youth</p>\n<p>6 - 12 years</p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">\n<p>Adult</p>\n<p>13+ years</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; height: 63px; width: 211px;\"><strong>Skis</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Blue</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">-</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£60</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Red</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">£43</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£83</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Black</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">-</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£99</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; height: 63px; width: 211px;\"><strong>Skis &amp; boots</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Blue</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">-</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£88</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Red</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 131px;\">£66</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£110</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 100px;\">Black</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 131px;\">-</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 112px;\">£127</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td valign=\"center\" style=\"height: 42px; text-align: center; width: 211px;\"><strong>Snowboard &amp; boots</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 42px; width: 100px;\">Red</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 42px; width: 131px;\">£66</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 42px; width: 112px;\">£110</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>Equipment information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Children 3 - 5 years can pre-book white skis and boots £66</li>\n<li>Free helmets for children up to 12 years when ski/board are pre-booked</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please see <a data-udi=\"umb://document/88813b4c856349a88af3cf6c8780d098\" href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/88813b4c856349a88af3cf6c8780d098}\" title=\"Ski Hire\">here</a> for a description of hire categories.</p>\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at the time of publishing. Up to date prices will be confirmed at the time of booking.</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "key": "91a633fd-d663-4968-a298-83c4c1c95c4c",
    "name": "Tuition",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "nC_SubTabs",
    "showSubTab": "1",
    "showInAccommodationPage": "1",
    "subtabTitle": "Tuition",
    "subTabDescription": "<p><strong>Tuition</strong></p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 233px; width: 665px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 43px;\">\n<th style=\"width: 78px; height: 43px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Ability</strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"width: 77px; height: 43px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Days / Times</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px; height: 43px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Adult (14+)</strong><strong><br /></strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px; height: 43px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Child (4-13 years)</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 75px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px; height: 75px;\">\n<p>Complete Beginner</p>\n<p><strong>(never skied before)</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px; height: 75px;\">\n<p>Mon-Fri</p>\n<p>11am - 12:50pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 75px;\">£185</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 75px;\">£185</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 78px;\">\n<p>Beginner</p>\n<p><strong>(able to snowplough turn on baby slope)</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px; height: 21px;\">\n<p>Mon-Fri</p>\n<p>10am - 12:50pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 21px; text-align: center; width: 49px;\">£225</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 21px;\">£225</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Inghams Exclusive Tuition</strong></p>\n<p>Our exclusive tuition is pre-bookable for children aged between 6-11 and is only available to Inghams guests. Children must be able to parallel turn on easy and medium slopes. Lunch is included in the cost. Guests will be met at the top of the Cretz lift and dropped back to the Hotel De Champoluc at the end of the day.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 124px; width: 667px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 78px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Ability</strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"width: 77px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Days / Times</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Child (6-11 years)</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px;\">\n<p><strong>Intermediate</strong></p>\n<p>Inghams Exclusive Tuition (lunch included)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px;\">\n<p>Mon - Fri</p>\n<p>9am - 3pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px;\">£549</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Private Tuition</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 670px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px;\">\n<p><strong>Private Ski Tuition</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px;\">\n<p>Mon 10am - 12pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px;\">\n<p>£120 (1 person)</p>\n<p>£30 each additional person</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p>Private tuition is available for ages 6+. Bookable for individuals or groups up to 4 of the same ability level.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Tuition information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tuition will be available all season </li>\n<li>Group tuition needs a minimum number of guests to take place. Very occasionally these numbers aren’t reached. If you have pre-booked tuition and this happens, the ski school will do their best to offer private tuition to the value of what you had originally booked.</li>\n<li>Snowboard tuition can be booked directly with the ski school - <span>Scuola Sci Champoluc</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at the time of publishing. Up to date prices will be confirmed at the time of booking.</strong></p>"
  },
  {
    "key": "4775f855-6251-4f0c-ac95-fbcfae2a1894",
    "name": "Ski Guiding & Free Ski Away Day",
    "ncContentTypeAlias": "nC_SubTabs",
    "showSubTab": "1",
    "showInAccommodationPage": "1",
    "subtabTitle": "Ski Guiding & Free Ski Away Day",
    "subTabDescription": "<p><strong>Ski Guiding</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy a stress-free tour of the local ski area and get your bearings on the first morning day of your holiday with a local qualified guide. Get insight into the best runs and places to ski on the mountain as well as some useful pointers along the way to improve technique.</p>\n<p>Groups are maximum 12 people and you must be at an intermediate level, confident and capable of skiing red runs. For just £20 per person, you can enjoy almost 3 hours of guiding. Places are limited, so please call us to book or add via 'My Booking' section of our website. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Free Ski Away Day</strong></p>\n<p>Pre-booked your 6 day lift pass? Great news, this grants you access to ski 2 days in another resorts within the Aosta Valley. Inghams have therefore arranged transport, so you can enjoy a day skiing elsewhere at no additional charge on one of the days - as long as you have a 6 day lift pass. Ski away days are weather dependant and the day and time will be advised locally. Please make sure you sign up before you go by either calling us or adding via 'My Booking' section of our website. </p>"
  }
]]]></skiExtrasSubTabs>
